# ─── Local development (.env) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Used by Vite dev server (npm run dev).
# In production (Docker / EKS) this value is set at BUILD TIME via:
#   docker build --build-arg VITE_API_URL=/api .
#
# During local development the Vite proxy (vite.config.js) forwards
# /api/* to http://localhost:8080, so /api is the correct value here too.
VITE_API_URL=/api
